// ============================================================================
// SPECTRUM COLOR DIFFERENCE FORMULAS
// ============================================================================
// Complete implementation of color difference metrics including CIE ΔE*ab,
// ΔE*94, ΔE*2000, CMC, ΔE*z (JzAzBz), and Oklab-based differences.
